column6: Buttons for reset and bootloader restart
10Kohm pullup resistor for the reset button
1.5Kohm LED Resistor and pullup for D-
2mm pitch 2x3 connector for ISP, pin headers
5.1Kohm resistor to tie CC of usb connector to ground
Power Fuse to avoid frying board
Anti Ghosting Diodes for the switch matrix
0.1uF capacitor for addressible LED power smoothing
